title: Filip Stamenković
text:
Filip Stamenković (; born 15 September 1998) is a <a href="Serbia">Serbia</a>n <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who plays for Russian club <a href="FC%20Veles%20Moscow">FC Veles Moscow</a>.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Veles%20Moscow">FC Veles Moscow</a> on 29 August 2021 in a game against <a href="FC%20Akron%20Tolyatti">FC Akron Tolyatti</a>.
